ecture","target":"../../../03-decisions/018-engine-extensibility-architecture","line":74},{"title":"../../../VAULT_RULES","target":"../../../VAULT_RULES","line":75},{"title":"../../../03-decisions/DECISION_LOG","target":"../../../03-decisions/DECISION_LOG","line":76},{"title":"../../../04-architecture/mockups/andura-clasic.html","target":"../../../04-architecture/mockups/andura-clasic.html","line":77},{"title":"../../../📥_inbox/HANDOVER_2026-05-13_CALENDAR_V1_S1_TO_S1_7_PLUS_STATUSLINE","target":"../../../📥_inbox/HANDOVER_2026-05-13_CALENDAR_V1_S1_TO_S1_7_PLUS_STATUSLINE","line":78},{"title":"../../concepts/calendar-feature-v1-spec","target":"../../concepts/calendar-feature-v1-spec","line":79}],"metadata":{"title":"ADR 020 — Storage Tiering Strategy (Tier 0/1/2 + Dexie.js + Rotation)","type":"entity","subtype":"adr","status":"locked-v1","locked_date":"2026-04-30","authority":"03-decisions/020-storage-tiering-strategy.md raw layer §Decision SSOT (Tier 0 localStorage Hot 30d + Tier 1 IndexedDB Dexie.js Warm 30-180d + Tier 2 Firebase Cold archive >180d) + §Library decision Dexie.js + §Rotation trigger pragmatic + §Migration runner one-time","voice_preservation":"synthesis + verbatim + bugatti + crossrefs","cross_refs":["[[adr-001-local-first-storage]]","[[adr-002-firebase-rest-not-sdk]]","[[adr-006-tier-storage-for-logs]]","[[adr-011-coach-decision-log-architecture]]","[[adr-018-engine-extensibility-architecture]]","[[../../concepts/append-only-architecture]]","[[../../concepts/calendar-feature-v1-spec]]","[[../engines/engine-coach-director]]"],"amendments":[{"date":"2026-05-13","note":"Tier 0 active rolling parity pattern S1.7 — `wv2-missing-equipment` localStorage key Calendar V1 missing equipment lifecycle dedicated picker permanent (10 echipamente standard gym toggle + `toggleEquipmentMissing()` + `hydrateAparateLipsa()` legacy RO normalize via `validIds` filter). Distinct semantic vs ephemeral Tier 0 rotation 30d auto-expire — user-driven edit oricând opt-out aparate selectate anterior (\"scoate aparatele care anterior selectate ca lipsa în caz că acum le ai\"). Path forward Coach Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13b","note":"S2 Production Wiring LANDED Tier 0 parity pattern preserved invariant — `wv2-missing-equipment` localStorage Tier 0 key propagated via `src/engine/coachContext.js` extend SSOT merge prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern engines absorb context (S2.B `fce846a`) + `src/ui/screens/aparateLipsa.js` modal overlay page port hydrate post-render legacy RO normalize via `validIds` filter (S2.C `a77587c`) + scheduleAdapter UI-side adapter filter consume Tier 0 list pre-build (S2.A `7c2f520`). User-driven edit oricând opt-in/opt-out preserved invariant (Daniel verbatim S1.7 *\"sa poti sa si scoti aparatele pe care anterior le-ai selectat ca nu e ai, in cazul in care acum le ai\"*). Distinct semantic vs ephemeral rotation 30d auto-expire reaffirm — Tier 0 = active rolling allows BOTH ephemeral time-bound AND permanent user-driven state. Tests 2914 → 2984 PASS (+70 net new) vitest cluster aparate-lipsa filter"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy.md"},"smart_blocks:wiki/entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"iabvju","at":1778657609978},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06316342,-0.05918049,0.01031869,-0.0491408,-0.000976,0.01387405,-0.05290373,-0.00475901,-0.01037047,0.01405,0.01265343,-0.04098019,0.02493545,0.04865807,0.02661862,0.00565272,-0.02442441,0.03773415,-0.02299234,0.04411326,0.07420649,-0.05872049,-0.02075217,-0.0360048,0.00284422,0.09255306,-0.06508442,-0.0147618,-0.11429926,-0.2418824,-0.03673608,-0.02750396,0.05256466,-0.00918086,-0.01036961,0.01794166,-0.03198913,0.06892372,-0.08033302,0.05550066,-0.04280835,0.02883421,-0.02734662,-0.04717975,-0.06203751,-0.02093088,-0.03380015,-0.00862085,-0.05075414,-0.03587057,-0.02422861,0.01264878,0.00106296,-0.00