m 30-180d + Tier 2 Firebase Cold archive >180d) + §Library decision Dexie.js + §Rotation trigger pragmatic + §Migration runner one-time","voice_preservation":"synthesis + verbatim + bugatti + crossrefs","cross_refs":["[[adr-001-local-first-storage]]","[[adr-002-firebase-rest-not-sdk]]","[[adr-006-tier-storage-for-logs]]","[[adr-011-coach-decision-log-architecture]]","[[adr-018-engine-extensibility-architecture]]","[[../../concepts/append-only-architecture]]","[[../../concepts/calendar-feature-v1-spec]]","[[../engines/engine-coach-director]]"],"amendments":[{"date":"2026-05-13","note":"Tier 0 active rolling parity pattern S1.7 — `wv2-missing-equipment` localStorage key Calendar V1 missing equipment lifecycle dedicated picker permanent (10 echipamente standard gym toggle + `toggleEquipmentMissing()` + `hydrateAparateLipsa()` legacy RO normalize via `validIds` filter). Distinct semantic vs ephemeral Tier 0 rotation 30d auto-expire — user-driven edit oricând opt-out aparate selectate anterior (\"scoate aparatele care anterior selectate ca lipsa în caz că acum le ai\"). Path forward Coach Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13b","note":"S2 Production Wiring LANDED Tier 0 parity pattern preserved invariant — `wv2-missing-equipment` localStorage Tier 0 key propagated via `src/engine/coachContext.js` extend SSOT merge prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern engines absorb context (S2.B `fce846a`) + `src/ui/screens/aparateLipsa.js` modal overlay page port hydrate post-render legacy RO normalize via `validIds` filter (S2.C `a77587c`) + scheduleAdapter UI-side adapter filter consume Tier 0 list pre-build (S2.A `7c2f520`). User-driven edit oricând opt-in/opt-out preserved invariant (Daniel verbatim S1.7 *\"sa poti sa si scoti aparatele pe care anterior le-ai selectat ca nu e ai, in cazul in care acum le ai\"*). Distinct semantic vs ephemeral rotation 30d auto-expire reaffirm — Tier 0 = active rolling allows BOTH ephemeral time-bound AND permanent user-driven state. Tests 2914 → 2984 PASS (+70 net new) vitest cluster aparate-lipsa filter"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy.md"},"smart_blocks:wiki/entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy.md#ADR 020 — Storage Tiering Strategy": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"qecwd5","at":1778657634427},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06180613,-0.0051215,-0.01711849,-0.00617939,-0.00451362,0.02903369,-0.06906487,-0.00680936,0.02756611,0.01281215,0.0365334,-0.06904226,0.01806665,0.04019574,0.01566186,0.00315426,-0.01541391,0.00879457,0.00229695,0.04281846,0.06252254,-0.05419741,-0.02568541,-0.04354529,0.00723161,0.07790938,-0.04776771,-0.0109705,-0.07636522,-0.24677666,-0.06221426,-0.05061073,0.08133958,0.01703456,-0.01736042,0.02259991,-0.02635149,0.03979733,-0.04063852,0.06660836,-0.06609344,0.06228707,-0.05994215,-0.00804213,-0.04332209,-0.03129001,-0.04182317,-0.0102998,-0.02830832,-0.00495909,-0.04303127,0.01930398,0.00313582,-0.00649603,0.02152341,0.00572697,0.06622812,0.05756987,0.03878063,0.06983982,0.03110073,-0.00668343,-0.21279365,0.05489108,-0.00100424,0.0467709,-0.01970911,-0.03638706,-0.02072502,0.0194637,-0.0085989,0.03353909,0.00595566,0.0290499,-0.02001862,-0.01416323,0.03331768,0.00045502,0.00807994,0.04113224,0.00865443,-0.01339743,-0.05634277,-0.00228602,-0.01819132,-0.02548878,0.04028841,0.02157077,0.04380205,-0.01939332,-0.00701437,0.00313504,0.08632143,-0.00744345,-0.02474404,0.0098303,0.00299395,0.06769458,-0.06052313,0.11106194,-0.0120426,0.02928773,0.02867729,0.01170771,0.02709054,-0.03071268,-0.00208569,-0.08191074,-0.03940115,-0.00060173,-0.00886652,0.03226426,0.04397194,-0.02487403,0.03795605,0.04651358,-0.00655613,0.04762461,-0.02673463,-0.00681323,-0.02366646,-0.01550635,0.02622269,-0.03054935,-0.02046433,0.03406053,0.04647147,0.05392475,0.00638895,0.06418101,0.00712301,0.02334484,-0.03955392,0.0423164,-0.01717467,-0.01679057,0.00804513,-0.03593889,0.04788658,-0.03136056,-0.03559549,-0